description: It has been almost 8 years, when our web solutions started with a small team. In 2010, we named ourselves as ‘Xaviera Techno Solutions’ – Your imagination, our creation. Enlightened with our epic rate of success and huge inflow of fresh projects, we decided to grow our team. Today, a team of highly experienced and versatile 20+ Creative Designers, 15+ Developers and 15+ Data Entry Operators work together to deliver you highly refined and splendid web service solutions. Approach us, let us know about your imaginations and aspirations, and we will help you effectuate them into a reality, almost instantaneously!
name: Xaviera Tech
